creator: Modus Group LLC
descriptionHtml:
ModusGo is a fleet management solution designed to help fleet and vehicle owners track, manage and optimize their fleet in real time.

Save time and money with metrics that matter. Streamline your operations and decrease fuel and maintenance costs. Be notified of vehicle health issues when they happen and receive alerts to schedule preventative maintenance, all which help you avoid costly down time. Drivers are given actionable insights to improve their safe driving behavior and reduce accidents.

With reporting on fuel fill-ups, fuel usage, time spent idling and vehicle efficiency, you can identify your greatest areas of needed improvement.

Improve management of your vehicles and mobile employees by always knowing where they are. Provide better customer service through destination alerts, boundary alerts and traffic tracking which will enable you to better estimate arrival and delivery times.
